{"tid":1612232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"除中槍男生，仲有2人危殆!!","createTime":"2019-10-02T07:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T12:58:40.000Z","uid":301152,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ecfa64892e2b4d51fe11d6df810d7faaf93d176d","tid":1612232,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"今早醫管局提供最新數字顯示，共104人送院，除了中槍的中五生曾志健，情況由危殆轉為穩定外，<span style=\"color: red;\">目前仍有兩名傷者留醫情況危殆。  </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫管局稱，截至今早10時，全港12間公立醫院共接收104名傷者，分別是81男23女，年齡介乎11至75歲。<br />\n  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">  現時兩名男子危殆，留醫東區醫院及律敦治醫院； </span>  <br />\n兩名男子嚴重；29人情況穩定或滿意（當中一人為曾志健），71人經治理後出院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191002&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60107233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191002%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60107233&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=8b0822c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191002%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60107233&h=87ec32f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191002&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60107233</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKtFgN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKtFgN3.png&h=cca25c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家關注下<br />\n<br />\n到底那2男子受咗咩傷致危殆？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好擔心啊"},{"pid":"90b5fa1ab7b624335f4a25ce9e73e0bf58